⚙️ What “delta-monitoring” really is

Not magic—just tracking change in a defined signal over time.

Define it explicitly:
	•	Signal S(t): what you’re measuring
	•	Context C(t): conditions around it
	•	Delta ΔS = S(t+1) − S(t)

If you don’t define S, you’re just vibe-tracking.

